{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Privacy Policy - Temp Fast Mail{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <section class="section">
        <div class="container has-text-centered">
            <div class="box">
                <h1 class="title">Privacy Policy for TempFastMail</h1>

                <p>
                    The following Privacy Policy refers to <strong>TempFastMail</strong>, a free-to-use web service and browser extension, hereinafter "TEMPFASTMAIL", available at
                    <a href="https://tempfastmail.com">https://tempfastmail.com</a>. It also covers <strong>TempFastMail Premium</strong> features on the web.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Our Commitment to Privacy</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL is committed to protecting your privacy. We will only use the information we collect in accordance with the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR) (Regulation (EU) 2016/679).
                    Using a temporary email protects your real mailbox from exposure. Your temporary email address is fully anonymous. Information such as your IP address and email communications is kept confidential.
                </p>

                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL does not store your IP address permanently. Emails and data are automatically deleted after a short period.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Services Overview</h2>
                <p>
                    <strong>TempFastMail Free:</strong> Provides temporary email addresses to receive emails. You can instantly change addresses or copy them to the clipboard. Emails are not stored for more than 48 hours.
                </p>

                <p>
                    <strong>TempFastMail Premium:</strong> Adds features like account registration. Only email addresses are collected for login and billing purposes.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Cookies and Tracking</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL uses cookies to track advertisements and remember user preferences. Third-party vendors, including <strong>Google</strong>, use cookies to serve ads based on prior visits. Users may opt out of personalized advertising via
                    <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads">Google Ads Settings</a>
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Google AdSense Disclosure</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL uses <strong>Google AdSense</strong> to serve advertisements. Google may use cookies to serve ads based on your previous visits to our website or other websites. The data collected includes:
                </p>
                <ul class="has-text-left">
                    <li>Browser type and settings</li>
                    <li>Device information and operating system</li>
                    <li>IP address (anonymized)</li>
                    <li>Time and date of visits</li>
                    <li>Referring website URLs</li>
                </ul>
                <p>
                    This information is used by Google and its partners to provide relevant ads to our users. Google may combine this data with other information collected from other websites. Users can opt out of personalized advertising through
                    <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads">Google Ads Settings</a>.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Third-Party Links</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL may contain links to third-party websites. These websites have their own privacy policies. We are not responsible for their content or practices.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Disclosure of Information</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL does not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to outside parties. We may share anonymous or aggregate data with trusted partners for analytics and advertising.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">California Privacy Rights</h2>
                <p>
                    California residents may request a list of third parties to whom personal information was disclosed for direct marketing purposes in the prior calendar year. TEMPFASTMAIL does not share personal information for third-party marketing.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Your Consent</h2>
                <p>
                    By using our website, you consent to this Privacy Policy.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Changes to Our Privacy Policy</h2>
                <p>
                    TEMPFASTMAIL may update this Privacy Policy. Changes will be posted on this page.
                </p>

                <h2 class="subtitle">Contact Us</h2>
                <p>
                    If you have any questions regarding this Privacy Policy or our services, contact us at:
                    <br>
                    Email: <a href="mailto:support@tempfastmail.com">support@tempfastmail.com</a><br>
                    TempFastMail Ltd.<br>
                </p>

                <br>
                <p><em>This policy is effective as of January 17, 2026</em></p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
{% endblock %}
